  <div class="content">
    <h3>Overview</h3>

    <p>
      Social Work              : Historical, theoretical and philosophical base of social work which includes the role of social work in the social welfare, modalities of practice, professional codes of ethics, and human rights legislation.          </p>

    <p class="catalog-terms">
      Terms:              Fall 2014          </p>

